# Backend Implementation for BMKG Amahai Website

Implement a functional backend for the existing Blade UI: database tables, Eloquent models, controllers, Form Request validation, XSS sanitization, rate limiting, secure file uploads, and clean routing.

## Proposed Changes

### Database Migrations

#### [NEW] [create_prakiraan_cuacas_table.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/database/migrations)
Table: `prakiraan_cuacas`
- `id`, `kecamatan` (string), `tanggal` (date), `jam` (string), `cuaca` (string), `suhu` (integer), `kelembaban` (integer), `angin_arah` (string), `angin_kecepatan` (integer), `icon` (string), `timestamps`

#### [NEW] [create_pegawais_table.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/database/migrations)
Table: `pegawais`
- `id`, `nama` (string), `jabatan` (string), `nip` (string unique), `pendidikan` (string), `golongan` (string), `foto` (string nullable — path to uploaded photo), `urutan` (integer default 0 — display order), `timestamps`

#### [NEW] [create_pengaduans_table.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/database/migrations)
Table: `pengaduans`
- `id`, `nama` (string), `nik` (string), `email` (string), `telepon` (string), `kategori` (string), `judul` (string), `isi` (text), `nomor_tiket` (string unique), `timestamps`

#### [NEW] [create_kritik_sarans_table.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/database/migrations)
Table: `kritik_sarans`
- `id`, `nama` (string nullable), `email` (string nullable), `jenis` (string — kritik/saran), `aspek` (string), `rating` (tinyInteger), `pesan` (text), `timestamps`

---

### Eloquent Models

#### [NEW] [PrakiraanCuaca.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Models/PrakiraanCuaca.php)
Mass-assignable fields, `$casts` for `tanggal` → `date`. Scope `scopeForToday()`.

#### [NEW] [Pegawai.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Models/Pegawai.php)
Mass-assignable fields, default ordering by `urutan`. Accessor for photo URL.

#### [NEW] [Pengaduan.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Models/Pengaduan.php)
Mass-assignable fields. Auto-generate `nomor_tiket` via model boot event.

#### [NEW] [KritikSaran.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Models/KritikSaran.php)
Mass-assignable fields.

---

### Form Request Validation (Security: no validation in controllers)

#### [NEW] [StorePengaduanRequest.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Requests/StorePengaduanRequest.php)
Rules:
- `nama`: required, string, max:255 — strip_tags sanitization
- `nik`: required, string, digits:16
- `email`: required, email, max:255
- `telepon`: required, string, regex:/^08\d{8,12}$/
- `kategori`: required, string, in:[list of valid categories]
- `judul`: required, string, max:255 — strip_tags sanitization
- `isi`: required, string, min:30, max:1000 — strip_tags sanitization
- `konfirmasi`: required, accepted

`passedValidation()` hook: sanitize string inputs via `strip_tags()` + `htmlspecialchars()`.

#### [NEW] [StoreKritikSaranRequest.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Requests/StoreKritikSaranRequest.php)
Rules:
- `nama`: nullable, string, max:255
- `email`: nullable, email, max:255
- `jenis`: required, in:kritik,saran
- `aspek`: required, string, in:[list of valid aspects]
- `rating`: required, integer, between:1,5
- `pesan`: required, string, min:20, max:2000

`passedValidation()` hook: sanitize via `strip_tags()`.

---

### Controllers

#### [NEW] [BerandaController.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Controllers/BerandaController.php)
`index()` — fetch today's weather data from `PrakiraanCuaca`, pass `$weatherCards` to `beranda` view. Falls back to hardcoded data if DB is empty.

#### [NEW] [PrakiraanCuacaController.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Controllers/PrakiraanCuacaController.php)
`index()` — group `PrakiraanCuaca` by `kecamatan` for today's date, pass `$kecamatans` to view. Falls back to the current hardcoded data as default.

#### [NEW] [PegawaiController.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Controllers/PegawaiController.php)
`index()` — fetch all `Pegawai` ordered by `urutan`, pass to view. Falls back to hardcoded data if table is empty.

#### [NEW] [PengaduanController.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Controllers/PengaduanController.php)
`create()` — return the form view.
`store(StorePengaduanRequest $request)` — save to DB, redirect back with success message + ticket number.

#### [NEW] [KritikSaranController.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/app/Http/Controllers/KritikSaranController.php)
`create()` — return the form view.
`store(StoreKritikSaranRequest $request)` — save to DB, redirect back with success message.

