### Blade View Updates

#### [MODIFY] [cuaca.blade.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/resources/views/pages/prakiraan/cuaca.blade.php)
Remove hardcoded `@php $kecamatans = [...]` block. The `$kecamatans` variable will now come from the controller.

#### [MODIFY] [sdm.blade.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/resources/views/pages/profil/sdm.blade.php)
Remove hardcoded `@php $pegawai = [...]` block. Add support for showing uploaded photo if `$p['foto']` exists. The `$pegawai` and `$jabatan_colors` will come from the controller.

#### [MODIFY] [pengaduan.blade.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/resources/views/pages/publik/pengaduan.blade.php)
Change `@submit.prevent="submitForm"` to real form POST submission. Show validation errors via `@error` directives. Keep Alpine JS for client-side UX but ensure the form actually submits to the server. Display `session('tiket')` for ticket number.

#### [MODIFY] [kritik-saran.blade.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/resources/views/pages/publik/kritik-saran.blade.php)
Same approach: real form POST + server-side validation errors + keep Alpine UX enhancements. Add `action="{{ url('/publik/kritik-saran') }}"` and hidden inputs for `jenis` and `rating`.

#### [MODIFY] [beranda.blade.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/resources/views/pages/beranda.blade.php)
Remove hardcoded `$weatherCards` array, use controller-provided variable instead.

