### Security Implementation

#### Rate Limiting (Throttle)
In [routes/web.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/routes/web.php), apply `->middleware('throttle:5,1')` to POST `/publik/pengaduan` — max 5 requests per minute per IP.

#### XSS Sanitization
Done in Form Request `passedValidation()` hooks using `strip_tags()` and `htmlspecialchars()`. Blade `{{ }}` already auto-escapes output.

#### SQL Injection Prevention
All DB queries use Eloquent (no `DB::raw()` or raw queries).

#### File Upload Security
SDM photo uploads (if added to admin later) validated via `mimes:jpg,jpeg,png` and `max:2048`. Stored in `storage/app/private/pegawai-photos` with symlink access.

---

### Routes Update

#### [MODIFY] [web.php](file:///e:/BMKG/WEBSITE/bmkg-amahai/routes/web.php)
Replace inline closures with controller methods:

```php
Route::get('/', [BerandaController::class, 'index'])->name('beranda');

Route::prefix('profil')->name('profil.')->group(function () {
    Route::get('/sdm', [PegawaiController::class, 'index'])->name('sdm');
    // sejarah, visi-misi, tugas-fungsi remain as view-only closures
});

Route::prefix('prakiraan')->name('prakiraan.')->group(function () {
    Route::get('/cuaca', [PrakiraanCuacaController::class, 'index'])->name('cuaca');
    // hasil-forecast remains as view-only closure
});

Route::prefix('publik')->name('publik.')->group(function () {
    Route::get('/pengaduan', [PengaduanController::class, 'create'])->name('pengaduan');
    Route::post('/pengaduan', [PengaduanController::class, 'store'])
        ->middleware('throttle:5,1')
        ->name('pengaduan.store');

    Route::get('/kritik-saran', [KritikSaranController::class, 'create'])->name('kritik-saran');
    Route::post('/kritik-saran', [KritikSaranController::class, 'store'])->name('kritik-saran.store');
    // survei remains as-is (redirect)
});
```

